How's this a plan ?
How we gonna get a car ?

241
00:16:07,792 --> 00:16:12,090
Sell that. I figure you can only have
painful association for Wash.

242
00:16:12,392 --> 00:16:16,690
"To Washington Bartholomew Hogwallop,

243
00:16:16,892 --> 00:16:18,290
from his lovin' Cora."

244
00:16:18,592 --> 00:16:23,690
- "Amor fidel... is."
- It was in his bureau,

245
00:16:23,992 --> 00:16:27,090
I reckon it'll fetch us enough
for a good auto voiture

246
00:16:27,292 --> 00:16:28,990
and a little leftover besides.

247
00:16:29,292 --> 00:16:31,590
Whoo ! You got light fingers, Everett.

248
00:16:31,892 --> 00:16:35,390
- Gopher ?
- You miserable little snake.

249
00:16:35,692 --> 00:16:37,390
You stole from my kin !

250
00:16:37,592 --> 00:16:39,990
Who was fixin' to betray us.

251
00:16:40,292 --> 00:16:42,190
You didn't know that at the time.

252
00:16:42,392 --> 00:16:44,390
So I borrowed it till I did know.

253
00:16:44,592 --> 00:16:46,490
That don't make no sense !

254
00:16:46,692 --> 00:16:49,390
A fool seeks logic
in the chambers of the heart.

255
00:16:49,692 --> 00:16:53,990
What the hell is that singing ?

256
00:16:55,392 --> 00:17:00,790
Appears to be some kind
of a... congregation.

257
00:17:00,992 --> 00:17:04,490
Care for some gopher ?

258
00:17:06,292 --> 00:17:07,990
No, thank you, Delmar.

259
00:17:08,192 --> 00:17:10,990
A third of a gopher'd
only arouse my appetite

260
00:17:11,292 --> 00:17:13,490
without beddin' her back down.

261
00:17:13,692 --> 00:17:15,890
Oh, you can have the whole thing.

262
00:17:16,192 --> 00:17:18,890
Me and Pete already had one.

263
00:17:19,192 --> 00:17:27,590
We ran across
a whole... gopher... village.

264
